name: In the Middle of the Noise, We Find Solitude.
description:
Dancing Manne Edition 1
@a.v.suals // Lilu Herlambang

Posterized Glitch, A3, 300 dpi.
Glitched in Signal Culture and cooked in Photoshop.

Dancing Manne is an exploration of the idea of how humans are just mannequins in this modern world; a puppet. Suggestible, compliant, easily influenced. 

Lilu Herlambang is a visual artist based in Bali, Indonesia. Coming from a background of photography and illustration, she is at the moment exploring glitch art and creative coding. Find more of her works in her website : aportofo.myportfolio.com
